data.description: This is a great house for you to call "home" in the growing community of Bondurant! Once you enter this home you will see brand new carpet and pad throughout, and your kitchen with plenty of counter and cabinet space for cooking and storage. The kitchen is open to your dining area and living room. The open space is perfect for entertaining guests along with the half bath and main level laundry! Upstairs you will find all 3 bedrooms with new carpet and pad, along with 2 full size bathrooms. The master suite even has a walk in closet and en-suite bath! Downstairs you will have an unfinished basement with an egress window that is ready for the new owner to finish! Outside you will notice your deck that leads to the fully fenced in backyard. The Wolf Creek HOA also offers a clubhouse with an in ground pool, perfect for next Summer!
